  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the security guard at a hospital. From your small office, you must watch the entire hospital through the security cameras. If you see a problem, you must run out and fix it! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/09f59cd342035622d504203762fa8ce0.webp?t=1749215186\" width=13 height=2 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/09f59cd342035622d504203762fa8ce0.webp?t=1749215186\" width=13 height=2 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/09f59cd342035622d504203762fa8ce0.webp?t=1749215186\" width=13 height=2 /></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/6e4d8e28ec76f0f5fbf397c47faffba8.apng?t=1749215186\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/6e4d8e28ec76f0f5fbf397c47faffba8.poster.avif?t=1749215186\" class=\"bb_img\" width=36 height=56 /></picture></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/93c2ff043fe2e4906aa364015890686d.webp?t=1749215186\" width=13 height=26 /></span>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/7e6442098b688841683f43b607d14081.avif?t=1749215186\" width=347 height=107 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/93c2ff043fe2e4906aa364015890686d.webp?t=1749215186\" width=13 height=26 /></span>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/3949eca07ce9a08d51cb1744cf29a690.apng?t=1749215186\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/3949eca07ce9a08d51cb1744cf29a690.poster.avif?t=1749215186\" class=\"bb_img\" width=54 height=114 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SO MANY STORIES!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every story is handwritten and designed. Some stories have multiple endings. Every story will be a unique experience. Nothing is randomly generated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/76c78d922f8171323605193dea6aa8d8.poster.avif?t=1749215186\" width=306 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/76c78d922f8171323605193dea6aa8d8.webm?t=1749215186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/87c678f9549e17d2d7fff73283500cf1.webp?t=1749215186\" width=65 height=2 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/d7845576646c97252ecf76cc8af3f995.apng?t=1749215186\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/d7845576646c97252ecf76cc8af3f995.poster.avif?t=1749215186\" class=\"bb_img\" width=62 height=56 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/93c2ff043fe2e4906aa364015890686d.webp?t=1749215186\" width=13 height=26 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/7370a5d3d4f74c6b2c0e3fbb7ba4b925.apng?t=1749215186\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/7370a5d3d4f74c6b2c0e3fbb7ba4b925.poster.avif?t=1749215186\" class=\"bb_img\" width=42 height=50 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SO MANY MONSTERS!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each story has its own monster, ghost, or other horrible being.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/93c2ff043fe2e4906aa364015890686d.webp?t=1749215186\" width=13 height=26 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/87c678f9549e17d2d7fff73283500cf1.webp?t=1749215186\" width=65 height=2 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/87c678f9549e17d2d7fff73283500cf1.webp?t=1749215186\" width=65 height=2 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/c97624bb5651ed6aeaa74fb11d5b68a6.poster.avif?t=1749215186\" width=32 height=58 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/c97624bb5651ed6aeaa74fb11d5b68a6.webm?t=1749215186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911390/extras/3639c6ec4d